Method Detail

activate

public void activate()
Activate this store. After a store is activated the childNames(int, IProgressMonitor) method will delegate its work to the slave store. If childNames(int, IProgressMonitor) is called without activating the store the cached names are returned.

isLocal

public boolean isLocal()
Determines if this file store is a local store. Local stores are stores that have a slave store comming from the EFS.getLocalFileSystem().

Returns:
True if this store is a local mount.
